item.title: Swats newest client (swat client v2) HELP!
item.dc:creator: @Volrom Volrom
item.description:
@Volrom wrote:

Well, he probably renamed the cache folder in C:\WINDOWS to something of his own. Either that or someone deleted the startup classes. That happened to me once, you are going to have to download the source again and the cache. Don’t rename it! Or just be careful if you do! Please +rep me if this was useful!

-Volrom
